ğŸ“¢ Traffic police crack down on lorries without speed limiters on the road
articles.content: A speed limiter is designed to limit the maximum speed that a vehicle can travel. Non-compliant lorries are prohibited from being driven, and their road tax cannot be renewed. We witnessed officers in action at several areas across Singapore, including Hougang, Sungei Kadut and Changi.

articles.content: After several weeks of thundery showers forecast, the second fortnight of January should turn "relatively drier", the Meteorological Service Singapore said on Friday (Jan 16).
